Class ConstrainString

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codename1.webrtc.ConstrainObject<String>
      • com.codename1.webrtc.ConstrainString
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JSONStruct

    public class ConstrainString
extends ConstrainObject<String>

    A constraint used by MediaTrackConstraints, AudioTrackConstraints, and VideoTrackConstraints to constrain the allowed values of certain constraints.

    <p>There are some static convenience methods in the RTC class for creating exact and ideal constraints.

    See Also:
    RTC.exact(java.lang.String), RTC.ideal(java.lang.String)
